data.description: This 2-unit solid brick building is an excellent investment opportunity you don't want to miss. Both units are fully occupied and generate consistent cash flow. The first-floor unit contains 2 bd/1bth, while the second-floor unit has 3bd/1bth. Each unit features spacious bedrooms, separate living and dining rooms, hardwood flooring, faux fireplaces that add to the property's charm, and many windows that allow abundant natural light. Additionally, each unit has an in-unit washer and dryer, an eat-in kitchen, laminate countertops, an enclosed back porch, and a large backyard that can also be used for parking. The property has separate utilities, a newer furnace and roof, and a full unfinished basement. It is conveniently located near public transportation, expressways, shopping, restaurants, grocery stores, and Jackson Park Hospital, making it a perfect location for tenants. Act quickly and call today to schedule your tour before it's too late!
